# 定义 

```cpp
class SString {
public:
    explicit SString(const char * cp);

    virtual ~SString();

private:
    char * data_;
};

// impl 
// 确保长度
SString::SString(const char * cp) : data_(new char[strlen(cp) + 1]) {
    strcpy(data_, cp);
}

SString::~SString() {
    delete[] data_;
}
```

> the rule of five 
> - Destructor
> - Copy Constructor
> - Copy Assignment Operator
> - Move Constructor
> - Move Assignment Operator


# `copy constructor`

