## 问题
1. use after free
2. double free 

## 解决方案 
> 实现copy constructor，避免两个指针指向一块内存地址

```cpp 

SString(const SString & other);

// impl
SString::SString(const SString & other) : data_(new char[strlen(other.data_) + 1]) {
    strcpy(data_, other.data_);
}

```

# `operator=`

